headline: FANG Teams With Halliburton & VoltaGrid to Deploy Electric Frac Fleets
summary: Diamondback, Halliburton and VoltaGrid collaborate to deploy electric simul-frac fleets in the Permian Basin, enhancing efficiency and reducing emissions.
